data.name: ReadDocument
data.value: select top(1) NAME, TYPE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATD_TSTAMP, DESCRIPTION, BUSINESS_OBJECT, RQURED_RSPNSE_DAYS, EVE_NO, EVD_ID, DETAILED_DESC, EFFECTIVE_DATE, EXPIRATION_DATE, PRINT_PREVIEW_SW, VERSION_NBR from CKT_DOCUMENT where (NAME = @name) and (EXPIRATION_DATE = @expirationDate) order by EXPIRATION_DATE desc

data.name: ReadEventEventDetail
data.value: select top(1) EVE_NO, SYSTEM_GENERATED_I, DETAIL_NAME from CKT_EVENT_DETAIL where (SYSTEM_GENERATED_I = @systemGeneratedI) and (EVE_NO = @eveNo)
